NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Role::ContributorSource - Something that finds and provides
    contributors.

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of
    Dist::Zilla::Role::ContributorSource - released April 25, 2014 as part
    of Dist-Zilla-Role-ContributorSource.

SYNOPSIS
        # in your Dist::Zilla thing...
        with 'Dist::Zilla::Role::ContributorSource';

        sub contributors { ... }

DESCRIPTION
    A simple interface role to define what plugins provide information about
    the contributors to the distribution, much as
    Dist::Zilla::Role::PrereqSource does for distribution prerequisites.

REQUIRED METHODS
  contributors
    Returns a list of the contributors sourced by this... thing. The list
    should be comprised of Dist::Zilla::Stash::Contributors::Contributor
    objects.

SEE ALSO
    Please see those modules/websites for more information related to this
    module.

    *   Dist::Zilla::Stash::Contributors

